<plot>A chorus girl (Marion Davies) gets bad advice from her fellow chorines in handling a rich suitor (Lawrence Gray) who assumes she is a gold-digger. But she assumes he is after "one thing" and is holding out for marriage. After meeting his mother, she learns that her beau is engaged to a society girl. He loses his money and they drift apart. But after making a new fortune, he comes to the theater.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?558464</url></doc>
